Many compliace has a requirement that that data must be replicated across greater distance
Cross Region replication allows data from s3 buckets to be replicated across the regions.

Important Pointer
Both the source and destination buckets must have the version enabled.

Create a replication rule in the source bucket.
- Mention the IAM role-name  and Region 

After uploading a object, it will take some time to get the object replicated in the destination region
